SIGN 50 32
The History about Zackaios

It all began in one of graals
dark nights. The loyal warrior
called Zackaios was out
in the rain. All over the streets
there was blood from a
slaughter. It was a full moon 
in the sky. I was on my way
to my girlfriend NaNouk. When
I suddenly heard strange sounds,
all I could see was rain and blood.
I began to walk faster. I was
ready with my sword. Then I
saw someone standing
still in front of my way. I could
not get a picture of the person.
- Hallo, who are you? I said
She looked into my eyes with
a cold blooded look. WAAAAH!
Next thing that happend was
that she was biting my neck.
I got a clear look in her face
before i fell down.
It was Moonie Darkmĺne.
When i woke up i felt a
new power inside of me.
I was now a Vampire.
Thats the story how the
warrior Zackaios became a cold
blooded mass killer. After that
he have fought many wars
in the name of
Ventrue Vampires
SIGNEND
